com.facebook.buck.dotnet

Class DotNetFramework

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.dotnet.DotNetFramework

  • public class DotNetFramework
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an instance of the .Net framework. Two instances are assumed to be equal iff they represent the same FrameworkVersion (notably, where that framework is installed is irrelevant).
